### Get all products (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all products (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?_page=1&_limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get product by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/22 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

